                            <comment id="17057553" author="lirui" created="Thu, 12 Mar 2020 03:01:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This is due to avro conflict between hive-exec and flink-shaded-hadoop-2-uber. In flink-shaded-hadoop-2-uber &lt;tt&gt;org/codehaus/jackson/JsonNode&lt;/tt&gt; is relocated. Therefore if we load &lt;tt&gt;Schema$Field&lt;/tt&gt; from flink-shaded-hadoop-2-uber, we&apos;ll get this NoSuchMethodError.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17111024" author="lzljs3620320" created="Tue, 19 May 2020 09:49:26 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;It should can be used with HADOOP_CLASSPATH. And we can consider shading also?&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
